---
title: Retro Turkey Burgers with Caramelized Onions and Potato Wedges
description: With caramelized onions, cheddar cheese, toasty buns and perfectly packed patties, this ready-in-a-flash turkey burger will make your weeknight dinner a delicious event!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/burgers-retro-a-la-dinde-526cca98.jpg
